compliant format.<br />\n			3. To produce compliant PDFs, use the &quot;Save as PDF&quot; feature which is built into MS Office 2010. Make sure that the following options are selected:<br />\n			-&nbsp;Optimize for: Standard (publishing online and printing)<br />\n			- Options &gt; PDF options &gt; Bitmap text when fonts may not be embedded<br />\n			<br />\n			4. Do not encrypt nor password-protect your PDF.</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n','2018-03-19 00:00:00','2018-03-19 00:00:00',NULL,6,'submission',1),(7,'<p><a href=\"http://icsse2017.hcmute.edu.vn/?ArticleId=707e0e24-5220-4821-a40f-4041eb76cc1a\">REGISTRATION&nbsp;</a></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>PAYMENT INSTRUCTIONS</strong><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>REGISTRATION FORM</p>\n\n<p><br />\nBefore you proceed with payment, you must fill in an ICSSE 2017 Registration Form. Check all items that you wish to purchase.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1</strong>.&nbsp;<strong>Click below&nbsp;button to fill&nbsp;ICSSE 2017&nbsp;<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/UZnb3jahWfyK6bSy1\" target=\"_blank\">Registration Form</a>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong><strong><a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/UZnb3jahWfyK6bSy1\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n<img alt=\"\"  height=\"50\" width=\"150\" width=\"auto\" src=\"http://icsse2017.hcmute.edu.vn/Resources/Images/SubDomain/icsse2017/CLICK-HERE-TO-REGISTER-ONLINE.png\" /></a></strong></strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>2.&nbsp;<a href=\"http://icsse2017.hcmute.edu.vn/Resources/Docs/SubDomain/icsse2017/ieeecopyrightform_ICSSE2017_paper.doc\">Click here to download&nbsp;the IEEE Copyright Form</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>MODES OF PAYMENT</strong></p>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong><strong>PAYMENT BY BANK TRANSFER:</strong></strong></p>\n\n<p>Please transfer the fee to the following bank account&nbsp;(Conference fee do NOT include bank transfer cost):<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Payee Name:&nbsp;</strong>TRUONG DAI HOC SU PHAM KY THUAT TP.HCM<br />\n<strong>Payee Address:&nbsp;</strong>01, VO VA