 Email: trungdt@hcmute.edu.vn<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>TAIWAN</strong><br />\r\nProf. Yo-Ping Huang - Email:&nbsp;yphuang@ntut.edu.tw<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n','2018-03-19 00:00:00','2018-03-19 00:00:00',NULL,13,'contact',1),(32,'<h2><strong>TTO - Ch v&agrave;i gi sau khi b&ecirc; bi r&ograve; r d liu ca 50 triu ngi d&ugrave;ng Facebook, tng t&agrave;i sn ca t ph&uacute; Mark Zuckerberg &atilde; ht hn 5 t USD v&igrave; c phiu c&ocirc;ng ty kh&ocirc;ng ngng lao dc.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2018/3/20/delete-facebook-techcrunch-15215355597781193344524.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"ng ch Facebook mt 5 t USD sau b bi l d liu ngi dng - nh 1.\" src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/784/2018/3/20/delete-facebook-techcrunch-15215355597781193344524.png\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>nh: TECHCRUNCH</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng nhng th, theo trang Sfgate, sau b&ecirc; bi, mt phong tr&agrave;o k&ecirc;u gi ty chay mng x&atilde; hi Facebook vi m&atilde; ch  #DeleteFacebook &atilde; tr&agrave;n ngp tr&ecirc;n mng x&atilde; hi Twitter k t ng&agrave;y 19-3 gi M.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&ugrave;ng vi m&atilde; ch  n&agrave;y, nhiu cu &quot;Facebooker&quot; c&ograve;n &quot; th&ecirc;m du v&agrave;o la&quot; vi nhng k nim bc bi tng gp tr&ecirc;n Facebook.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Tt c ch&uacute;ng ta u ra ri khi MySpace, ch&uacute;ng ta cng c&oacute; th ri khi Facebook&quot;, t&agrave;i khon @ecarpen vit. Trong khi &oacute; t&agrave;i khon @FinnDen &quot;bi&quot; th&ecirc;m: &quot;Facebook kh&ocirc;ng phi c&aacute;i nh ch&uacute;ng ta &atilde; ngh&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;H&atilde;y b ngay Facebook h&ocirc;m nay. H&atilde;y h&agrave;nh ng &uacute;ng ngay t u. Kh&ocirc;ng th hn na&quot;, t&agrave;i khon @jmdsouza67 hiu triu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cui tun qua, t New York Times &atilde; l&agrave; mt trong nhng ni u ti&ecirc;n phanh phui s vic d liu ca 50 triu ngi d&ugrave;ng Facebook b c&ocirc;ng ty ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch d liu ch&iacute;nh tr Cambridge Analytica thu thp v&agrave; khai th&aacute;c theo hng phc v cho chin dch tranh c ca t ph&uacute; Donald Trump nm 2016.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C th, Cambridge Analytica &atilde; nhn 15 triu USD ca &ocirc;ng Robert Mercer, nh&agrave; t&agrave;i tr ng Cng h&ograve;a, t trc t bu c gia nhim k nm 2014 n tr cho &ocirc;ng Aleksandr Kogan, gi&aacute;o s i hc Cambridge v&agrave; c&oacute; c d liu ca h&agrave;ng triu ngi d&ugrave;ng Facebook.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trc &oacute; &ocirc;ng Kogan &atilde; tr tin cho khong 270.000 ngi  h in v&agrave;o mt mu thm d&ograve; tr&ecirc;n mng, x&acirc;y dng bng c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng c ph&aacute;t trin ca Facebook, gi&uacute;p &ocirc;ng nm c th&ocirc;ng tin v c&aacute;c trang h &atilde; &quot;like&quot;, c xem danh s&aacute;ch bn b&egrave; ca h&hellip;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ging nh hu ht nhng ngi gi&agrave;u nht th gii, t&agrave;i sn r&ograve;ng ca t ph&uacute; Mark Zuckerberg c quyt nh phn ln bi vic tng/gim im ca th trng chng kho&aacute;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T&iacute;nh ti rng s&aacute;ng 19-3, c phiu ca Facebook &atilde; gim 8%, theo &oacute; cho ti tra c&ugrave;ng ng&agrave;y, danh s&aacute;ch cp nht &quot;C&aacute;c t ph&uacute; th gii&quot; ca Forbes cho bit t&agrave;i sn r&ograve;ng ca t ph&uacute; Zuckerberg c&ograve;n khong 69,5 t USD, gim &aacute;ng k so vi mc 75 t USD v&agrave;o thi im th trng &oacute;ng ca ng&agrave;y th s&aacute;u (16-3).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo d liu ca Forbes, ch trong v&agrave;i gi ng&agrave;y 19-3 gi M, t&agrave;i sn ca &ocirc;ng Zuckerberg &atilde; gim khong 6,7%, tng ng vi khong 5,1 t USD.</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><strong>Nu mun x&oacute;a t&agrave;i khon Facebook</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhng ai mun x&oacute;a s t&agrave;i khon Facebook cn bit l&agrave; h s phi ch ti 3 th&aacute;ng  c&oacute; th dn sch s mi d liu c&aacute; nh&acirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vi nhng ngi ch&aacute;n ng&aacute;n Facebook v&agrave; chn c&aacute;ch tm thi &quot;deactivate&quot; (ngng k&iacute;ch hot t&agrave;i khon), h cng n&ecirc;n bit l&agrave; vi la chn n&agrave;y, mng x&atilde; hi s kh&ocirc;ng hin th nhng th&ocirc;ng tin ca ch t&agrave;i khon vi bn b&egrave; h, nhng iu &oacute; cng kh&ocirc;ng ngn cn c vic d liu c&aacute; nh&acirc;n ca h c&oacute; th b li dng cho mc &iacute;ch kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhng ngi d&ugrave;ng Facebook cng c&oacute; th ti v  lu li c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin c chia s tr&ecirc;n Facebook trc khi x&oacute;a t&agrave;i khon bng c&aacute;ch: V&agrave;o Settings - General - Download a Copy of Your Facebook Data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D liu lu ca bn tr&ecirc;n Facebook s c gi ti ngi d&ugrave;ng qua email.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p> x&oacute;a t&agrave;i khon Facebook, bn v&agrave;o &quot;Settings&quot;- t&igrave;m ti phn &quot;Manage account,&quot; chn &quot;Edit&quot; sau &oacute; bm v&agrave;o &quot;Request account deletion&quot; ri l&agrave;m theo c&aacute;c bc hng dn.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n','2018-03-20 20:22:38','2018-03-20 20:22:38','ng ch Facebook mt 5 t USD sau b bi l d liu ngi dng',14,'news',1),(33,'<p>Chic in thoi ri xung l&agrave;m &aacute;m l&aacute; kh&ocirc; tung l&ecirc;n tht p v&agrave; Galaxy S9 &atilde; ghi trn khonh khc n&agrave;y - Clip: K.VY</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Vi GalaxyS9, quay chm kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n l&agrave; k xo in nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Slow-motion l&agrave; k thut quay video vi hiu ng l&agrave;m chm c&aacute;c h&agrave;nh ng, thc cht l&agrave; kh nng chp rt nhiu khung nh trong 1 gi&acirc;y  c&oacute; th c t h&agrave;nh ng rt chi tit ca i tng c ghi h&igrave;nh. K thut n&agrave;y c s dng rt nhiu trong k xo in nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vi s ph&aacute;t trin ca c&ocirc;ng ngh camera tr&ecirc;n in thoi th&ocirc;ng m&igrave;nh nh Galaxy S9|S9+, c&aacute;c thc phim si&ecirc;u chm (super slomo) kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n gii hn  c&aacute;c nh&agrave; l&agrave;m phim chuy&ecirc;n nghip m&agrave; bt k ai cng c&oacute; th l&agrave;m c c&aacute;c thc phim n&agrave;y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh o din Nguyn Quang Dng n&oacute;i vui ti hi tho K nguy&ecirc;n giao tip bng h&igrave;nh nh va t