n bit v&agrave; bt trn khonh khc chuyn ng vi kh nng chp 960 khung h&igrave;nh tr&ecirc;n 1 gi&acirc;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video khi quay xong s n&eacute;n chun mp4 v&agrave; t ng lng nhc v&agrave;o hoc ngi d&ugrave;ng ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n ch ng chn nhc lng theo s th&iacute;ch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2018/3/20/photo-1-1521545816060356430445.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"T to video quay chm vi Super Slow Motion trn Galaxy S9 - nh 4.\" src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/784/2018/3/20/photo-1-1521545816060356430445.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau &oacute; v&agrave;o &quot;Chi tit&quot;  chn nhc nn - nh: T.TNG</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bn cng c&oacute; th ct cup clip theo &yacute; th&iacute;ch trong phn chnh sa video, o ngc chuyn ng, to v&ograve;ng lp trong chi tit video, th l&agrave; xong v&agrave; vic c&ograve;n li l&agrave; up l&ecirc;n mng chia s c&ugrave;ng bn b&egrave; m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn phi s dng mt phn mm dng phim n&agrave;o c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2018/3/20/photo-2-1521545816066641380679.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"T to video quay chm vi Super Slow Motion trn Galaxy S9 - nh 5.\" src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/784/2018/3/20/photo-2-1521545816066641380679.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>V&agrave; chn ct  chnh sa clip - nh: T.TNG</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch vi v&agrave;i thao t&aacute;c n gin, c&acirc;u chuyn h&igrave;nh nh quay chm &atilde; c bt trn y ngh thut nh k xo in nh v&agrave; bi&ecirc;n dng d d&agrave;ng hn bao gi ht. V&agrave; di &acirc;y l&agrave; clip ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i &atilde; th tri nghim</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video tm dng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chuyn ng ca xe c tr&ecirc;n ng ph &atilde; c ghi li trn vn vi chc nng quay si&ecirc;u chm tr&ecirc;n Galaxy S9 - Clip: THI&Ecirc;N TNG</p>\r\n\r\n<p>on video quay si&ecirc;u chm c ghi 0.2 gi&acirc;y v&agrave; ph&aacute;t li trong 6 gi&acirc;y. Galaxy S9 cho ph&eacute;p mt clip quay c ti a 20 on super slow motion   ph&acirc;n gii HD 720P, bitrate khong tr&ecirc;n 11.000 kbps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video tm dng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhng a tr vui &ugrave;a tr&ecirc;n h Tr An tht th&uacute; v - Clip: PHM AN DNG</p>\r\n','2018-03-20 23:36:32','2018-03-20 23:36:32','T to video quay chm vi Super Slow Motion trn Galaxy S9',14,'news',1),(34,'<h2>TTO - H&atilde;ng c&ocirc;ng ngh IBM va tr&igrave;nh l&agrave;ng mu m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh nh nht th gii, nh hn ht mui nhng li c t&iacute;ch hp c&ocirc;ng ngh &ldquo;<em>thi </em>thng&rdquo; blockchain.</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://congnghe.tuoitre.vn/thiet-bi-so/blackberry-hop-tac-samsung-gioi-thieu-tablet-bao-mat-secutablet-720854.htm\">BlackBerry hp t&aacute;c Samsung, IBM gii thiu SecuTABLET</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://congnghe.tuoitre.vn/nhip-song-so/ibm-google-hop-tac-giup-tang-hieu-suat-may-chu-len-10-lan-1188337.htm\">IBM, Google hp t&aacute;c gi&uacute;p tng hiu sut m&aacute;y ch l&ecirc;n 10 ln</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://congnghe.tuoitre.vn/thiet-bi-so/ibm-san-xuat-duoc-thiet-bi-luu-tru-du-lieu-sieu-khong-lo-20170810163754582.htm\">IBM sn xut c thit b lu tr d liu si&ecirc;u khng l</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2018/3/20/may-tinh-nho-bang-hat-muoi-ibm-1521514345028582705946.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"IBM ra mt my tnh nh hn ht mui - nh 1.\" src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/784/2018/3/20/may-tinh-nho-bang-hat-muoi-ibm-1521514345028582705946.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M&aacute;y t&iacute;nh nh nht th gii - nh: IBM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo trang tin Mashable, ng&agrave;y 19-3, ti hi ngh c&ocirc;ng ngh cao cp IBM Think 2018 ca IBM, c&ocirc;ng ty n&agrave;y &atilde; ln u ra mt sn phm c tuy&ecirc;n b l&agrave; m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh nh nht th gii.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>R&otilde; r&agrave;ng IBM &atilde; kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; li trong th&ocirc;ng tin qung b&aacute; bi mu m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh h gii thiu c&oacute; k&iacute;ch thc thm ch&iacute; c&ograve;n nh hn mt ht mui.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n ng  k&iacute;ch thc &aacute;nh la, bi thit b n&agrave;y c&oacute; nng lc x l&yacute; th&ocirc;ng tin mnh m tng ng vi mt con chip x86 ca nhng nm 1990. V&agrave;  nh&igrave;n thy n&oacute;, bn s phi d&ugrave;ng ti k&iacute;nh hin vi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo IBM, chi ph&iacute; sn xut m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh si&ecirc;u t&iacute; hon n&agrave;y cha ti 10 cent v&agrave; n&oacute; gm &quot;v&agrave;i trm ng&agrave;n b&oacute;ng b&aacute;n dn&quot;. Theo &oacute; n&oacute; c&oacute; kh nng &quot;theo d&otilde;i, ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch, li&ecirc;n lc v&agrave; thm ch&iacute; x l&yacute; tr&ecirc;n d liu&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vi nhng ngi quan t&acirc;m ti bitcoin, h c&agrave;ng c&oacute; l&yacute; do hn  t&igrave;m hiu v mu m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh nh nht th gii ca IBM v&igrave; thit b n&agrave;y t&iacute;ch hp c&ocirc;ng ngh blockchain, mt c&ocirc;ng ngh nn tng ca tin in t.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/2018/3/20/mo-phong-may-tinh-sieu-nho-ibm-15215143647061906865531.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"IBM ra mt my tnh nh hn ht mui - nh 2.\" src=\"https://cdn.tuoitre.vn/thumb_w/784/2018/3/20/mo-phong-may-tinh-sieu-nho-ibm-15215143647061906865531.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bn m&ocirc; phng thit k m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh nh nht th gii - nh: IBM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>M&aacute;y t&iacute;nh si&ecirc;u nh s l&agrave; ngun d liu phc v cho c&aacute;c ng dng ca c&ocirc;ng ngh blockchain. Nhng tim nng ng dng ca n&oacute; bao gm theo d&otilde;i vic vn chuyn h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a, ph&aacute;t hin t&igrave;nh hung trm cp, gi mo, kh&ocirc;ng tu&acirc;n th quy nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra n&oacute; cng c&oacute; th thc hin c&aacute;c thao t&aacute;c c bn li&ecirc;n quan ti tr&iacute; tu nh&acirc;n to nh ph&acirc;n loi d liu c cung cp.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo IBM, &acirc;y mi ch l&agrave; th&agrave;nh qu bc u. Trong v&ograve;ng 5 nm ti, nhng thit b c&ocirc;ng ngh vi k&iacute;ch thc si&ecirc;u nh s c&ograve;n c n&acirc;ng cp v&agrave; ng dng rng r&atilde;i hn trong c&aacute;c h thng v&agrave; vt dng h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y.</p>\r\n','2018-03-20 23:40:09','2018-03-20 23:40:32','IBM ra mt my tnh nh hn ht mui',14,'news',1),(36,'EMPTY','2018-03-20 23:42:26','2018-03-20 23:42:26','EMPTY',14,'news',1),(37,'<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://docs.google.com/uc?id=1fNGvL-5i4OCpHhLyvTy3DCx7SpqF5Xgb\" style=\"height:889px; width:500px\" /></p>\r\n','2018-03-20 23:57:48','2018-03-20 23:57:48','Insert ',14,'news',1),(38,'<p><strong>NOT EMPTY&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n','2018-03-21 16:06:59','2018-03-25 22:00:22','EMPTY',14,'news',1),(42,'<p>TEST</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1vBbwYv1HEcIlEbUno_2xfEYalh9To2V-&amp;export=download\" style=\"height:292px; width:500px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1vBbwYv1HEcIlEbUno_2xfEYalh9To2V-&amp;export=download</p>\r\n','2018-03-26 05:00:42','2018-03-25 22:02:15','NEWS',14,'news',1);
